{"url": "https://people.com/style/kris-jenner-explains-blonde-pixie/", "text": "Kris Jenner is finally explaining why we\u2019ve seen her sporting a platinum blonde pixie.\n\nOn an upcoming episode of Keeping Up with the Kardashians, the momager sits in her glam room after getting her hair done and shows off her bold new look to Kim Kardashian. \u201cWhat is going on?\u201d Kardashian says as she sees her mom\u2019s new \u2018do, which is the same icy tone as her own blonde hair.\n\n\u201cDo you like it?\u201d Jenner asks. \u201cI think it looks really great,\u201d Kardashian replied. But Jenner quickly clarified that it wasn\u2019t a permanent change.\n\n\u201cI\u2019ve really wanted to go blonde for so long, but the process is really grueling on your hair that I thought I would try a wig first.\u201d\n\nAfter checking out her mom\u2019s bold new look for a few minutes, Kardashian realized exactly who Jenner looked like as a blonde.\n\nLooking for more style content? Click here to subscribe to the PeopleStyle Newsletter for amazing shopping discounts, can\u2019t-live-without beauty products and more.\n\n\u201cHave you ever seen the movie The Devil Wears Prada? You kind of look like Miranda Priestly [played by Meryl Streep],\u201d Kardashian says. \u201cIt takes a really strong woman to pull off this icy blonde.\u201d\n\nAnd it seems like Jenner was pretty pleased with that comparison. \u201cMiranda Priestly represents this amazing chicness and New York attitude and now I am looking in the mirror and Kim is right. I mean, we are the same person!\u201d Jenner says. \u201cI could get used to this.\u201d\n\nKim Kardashian/Instagram\n\n\u201cWelcome to the club!\u201d Kardashian, who dyed her hair platinum last September, replies to her mom.\n\nBlonde Jenner first broke the internet in Kim Kardashian\u2019s Instagram last October of her looking ridiculously glamorous while holding a martini glass in a red floral outfit with fur stole. She also kicked off 2018 with a reappearance of the blonde thanks to KarJenner hair pro Chris Appleton.\n\nRELATED PHOTOS: UPDATED! Must-See Celebrity Hair Changes\n\n\u201cJanuary 2nd back at work here we go!!!\u201d Jenner captioned the photo of her \u2018do, adding #happynewyear2018.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/5Pp0tsig5GjnIcjMChCKlvdWI4w=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/prince-harry-meghan-markle-kris-jenner-kim-kardashian-birthday2-111125-f2a00c2d35b24b32bf353aebebfed03c.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/43_WEh9L6Vcv6QB8_2_WILE1NZY=/343x228/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Meghan-Markle-090824-4ab64512d0f245299e8a82b3c31f2b12.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/EKlxP0gNpam0YcjHBNxV0IkpMUQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/prince-harry-serena-williams-meghan-markle-baby2baby-gala-west-hollywood-111025-d2d224a5d9a445b9839798ef38914e9d.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/A_LxI4wCE5jWP3OsQ2pHt2MRymA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/jenna-bush-hager-haircut-2-111125-2502707467d94c739b45b2906a2a898e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/rzVUXIhYi612lDWTrQvq0c60KYs=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/king-charles-sharon-osbourne-111225-a03f22129e964f02b9100188435196f2.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/gDqFIgMiD4lPy2c-2nO2sse_uUc=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(256x0:258x2)/kris-19b50114aef245b7bd3a427e3203e53d.png", "https://people.com/thmb/aJXo7HEFm7oF8YflyVvf351zM9o=/200x200/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Headshot-2000-ca8c28b4e983413d8ad4635965a0a09e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/-68DUJuftwoQ35VahbBP76TWrKM=/4000x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(256x0:258x2)/kris-19b50114aef245b7bd3a427e3203e53d.png", "https://people.com/thmb/Uo8iLTyanrj7eNHYmSXZHwHJbxY=/800x533/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Spencer-Lofranco-112025-56efb2cd379b4817ac0f4d3b10fb37f3.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/G_DPL9OV6vFY_H1